The building remained flexible and light, despite the limitations, challenges and transformations.
Kri<0xC5><0xA1>anitz recently noted that the pavilion “from Brussels” was rude – a typical story of “a drop in the city”.
Such architecture is "always out of place" and nevertheless wants to "stimulate real awareness".
