Slogans concerning China, Iran and aid to Israel are often confused with each other.
Mitt Romney, who has the best chance of being nominated by the “Old Good Party”, threatened to file a complaint against the Chinese at the WTO and accuse them of “manipulating their currency is a sensitive topic for America, annoyed by the migration of entire industries to Asia.
